rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0001
rows.name:
Before we board the ferry at
Yajika Harbor, we should take
care of that ether miasma.

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0003
rows.name: Yes! Please leave it to me!

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0005
rows.name:
If it's going to cause trouble for
someone down the line, isn't it
better that we deal with it now?

rows.label: campfev11_0500_msg0007
rows.name:
Well... I am curious about
Kasumi's ether-manipulation
powers, so I guess I'll tag along.
